      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Aleš Zamuda</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:163px;\"><a href=\"https://labraj.feri.um.si/en/Ale%c5%a1_Zamuda\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/b/b4/AlesZamuda.jpg\" width=\"161\" height=\"230\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:AlesZamuda.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Aleš Zamuda <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Aleš Zamuda</b>,<br />\na Slovenian computer scientist and assistant professor at <i>Computer Architecture and Languages Laboratory</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, Institute of Computer Science at <a href=\"/University_of_Maribor\" title=\"University of Maribor\">University of Maribor</a>, where he received his B.Sc., M.Sc., and Ph.D. degrees in 2006, 2008, and 2012, respectively. \nHis research interests include <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multi-objective_optimization\">multi-objective optimization</a>, \n<a href=\"/Genetic_Programming#EvolutionaryComputation\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">evolutionary computation</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Differential_evolution\">differential evolution</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_life\">artificial life</a>, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_animation\">computer animation</a>. \nHe is inventor of <i>Differential Evolution for Parameterized Procedural Woody Plant Models Reconstruction within Environmental Framework to Visualize Emergent Artificial Forest Ecosystems</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, an approach for reconstruction of procedural three-dimensional models of woody plants (trees). also topic of his Ph.D. thesis <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\nAs computer games programmer, Aleš is author of the <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/QuTeChess\" title=\"QuTeChess\">QuTeChess</a> under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GNU General Public License</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>, and further wrote <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Reversi</a> and <a href=\"/Connect_Four\" title=\"Connect Four\">Connect Four</a> programs <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2007_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ale%C5%A1_Zamuda&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2007_...\">2007 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ale%C5%A1_Zamuda&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2007 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a>, <a href=\"/Janez_Brest\" title=\"Janez Brest\">Janez Brest</a>, <a href=\"/Borko_Bo%C5%A1kovi%C4%87\" title=\"Borko Bošković\">Borko Bošković</a>, <a href=\"/Viljem_%C5%BDumer\" title=\"Viljem Žumer\">Viljem Žumer</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/4424941?arnumber=4424941\">Differential Evolution for Multiobjective Optimization with self Adaptation</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Congress on Evolutionary Computation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Janez_Brest\" title=\"Janez Brest\">Janez Brest</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a>, <a href=\"/Borko_Bo%C5%A1kovi%C4%87\" title=\"Borko Bošković\">Borko Bošković</a>, <a href=\"/Sa%C5%A1o_Greiner\" title=\"Sašo Greiner\">Sašo Greiner</a>, <a href=\"/Viljem_%C5%BDumer\" title=\"Viljem Žumer\">Viljem Žumer</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-68830-3_3\">An Analysis of the Control Parameters’ Adaptation in DE</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-3-540-68830-3\">Advances in Differential Evolution</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Borko_Bo%C5%A1kovi%C4%87\" title=\"Borko Bošković\">Borko Bošković</a>, <a href=\"/Sa%C5%A1o_Greiner\" title=\"Sašo Greiner\">Sašo Greiner</a>, <a href=\"/Janez_Brest\" title=\"Janez Brest\">Janez Brest</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a>, <a href=\"/Viljem_%C5%BDumer\" title=\"Viljem Žumer\">Viljem Žumer</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F978-3-540-68830-3_12\">An Adaptive Differential Evolution Algorithm with Opposition-Based Mechanisms, Applied to the Tuning of a Chess Program</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-3-540-68830-3\">Advances in Differential Evolution</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ale%C5%A1_Zamuda&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Borko_Bo%C5%A1kovi%C4%87\" title=\"Borko Bošković\">Borko Bošković</a>, <a href=\"/Janez_Brest\" title=\"Janez Brest\">Janez Brest</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a>, <a href=\"/Sa%C5%A1o_Greiner\" title=\"Sašo Greiner\">Sašo Greiner</a>, <a href=\"/Viljem_%C5%BDumer\" title=\"Viljem Žumer\">Viljem Žumer</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1966601\">History mechanism supported differential evolution for chess evaluation function tuning</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springer.com/engineering/computational+intelligence+and+complexity/journal/500\">Soft Computing</a>, Vol. 15, No. 4</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a>, <a href=\"/Janez_Brest\" title=\"Janez Brest\">Janez Brest</a>, <a href=\"/Borko_Bo%C5%A1kovi%C4%87\" title=\"Borko Bošković\">Borko Bošković</a>, <a href=\"/Viljem_%C5%BDumer\" title=\"Viljem Žumer\">Viljem Žumer</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S156849461100247X\">Differential Evolution for Parameterized Procedural Woody Plant Models Reconstruction</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.journals.elsevier.com/applied-soft-computing\">Applied Soft Computing</a>, Vol. 11, No. 8</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Differential Evolution for Parameterized Procedural Woody Plant Models Reconstruction</i>. Ph.D. thesis. Faculty of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science,  <a href=\"/University_of_Maribor\" title=\"University of Maribor\">University of Maribor</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a>, <a href=\"/Janez_Brest\" title=\"Janez Brest\">Janez Brest</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0020025512005038\">Environmental Framework to Visualize Emergent Artificial Forest Ecosystems</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_Sciences_(journal)\">Information Sciences</a>, Vol. 220</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a>, <a href=\"/Janez_Brest\" title=\"Janez Brest\">Janez Brest</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0020025514004927\">Vectorized Procedural Models for Animated Trees Reconstruction using Differential Evolution</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_Sciences_(journal)\">Information Sciences</a>, Vol. 278</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ale%C5%A1_Zamuda&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a>, <a href=\"/Janez_Brest\" title=\"Janez Brest\">Janez Brest</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S2210650215000826\">Self-adaptive control parameters' randomization frequency and propagations in differential evolution</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.journals.elsevier.com/swarm-and-evolutionary-computation\">Swarm and Evolutionary Computation</a>, Vol. 25 </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Adaptive constraint handling and Success History Differential Evolution for CEC 2017 Constrained Real-Parameter Optimization</i>. CEC 2017</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ale%C5%A1_Zamuda&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://labraj.feri.um.si/en/Ale%c5%a1_Zamuda\">Aleš Zamuda - Computer Architecture and Languages Laboratory</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=2FM-GygAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Aleš Zamuda - Google Scholar Citations</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://si.linkedin.com/in/aleszamuda\">Ales Zamuda | LinkedIn</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ale%C5%A1_Zamuda&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://labraj.feri.um.si/en/Ale%c5%a1_Zamuda\">Aleš Zamuda - Computer Architecture and Languages Laboratory</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://labraj.feri.um.si/en/General_Information\">Computer Architecture and Languages Laboratory</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://labraj.feri.um.si/en/International_invention_fair_SIIF_2012\">International invention fair SIIF 2012 - Computer Architecture and Languages Laboratory</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aleš Zamuda</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Differential Evolution for Parameterized Procedural Woody Plant Models Reconstruction</i>. Ph.D. thesis. Faculty of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science,  <a href=\"/University_of_Maribor\" title=\"University of Maribor\">University of Maribor</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"re